299
00:27:54,956 --> 00:27:56,635
Heart is deaf.

300
00:27:58,320 --> 00:27:59,166
Heart.

301
00:28:02,294 --> 00:28:05,836
This big bro, his name is…

302
00:28:12,867 --> 00:28:13,756
Nice to meet you too.

303
00:28:15,409 --> 00:28:20,216
So, how did you come to work here?

304
00:28:21,647 --> 00:28:23,647
A senior at my school told me about this job.

305
00:28:23,647 --> 00:28:25,581
So I asked Heart to join me.

306
00:28:25,931 --> 00:28:27,810
It's a change of scenery that also pays.

307
00:28:29,584 --> 00:28:30,918
Self-made teens, huh?

308
00:28:32,323 --> 00:28:34,507
I want to save money for the Work & Travel program.

309
00:28:34,887 --> 00:28:36,450
So I don't have to ask Uncle Jim for it.

310
00:28:40,799 --> 00:28:43,901
Is he okay with that though?

311
00:28:45,026 --> 00:28:46,047
He is.

312
00:28:47,026 --> 00:28:49,681
What about you? I haven’t seen you come to work at the diner.

313
00:28:49,681 --> 00:28:50,977
It's been a while.

314
00:28:53,840 --> 00:28:54,690
Well…

315
00:28:56,022 --> 00:28:59,810
Your uncle said that the diner hasn't been very busy lately.

316
00:28:59,810 --> 00:29:00,722
I don’t have to be there.

317
00:29:00,722 --> 00:29:04,471
That's not true. It’s so busy.

318
00:29:05,814 --> 00:29:09,467
Anyway, Gaipa is helping us at the diner now.

319
00:29:13,154 --> 00:29:13,960
That’s nice.

320
00:29:33,631 --> 00:29:35,034
Could you take a picture of us?

321
00:29:36,662 --> 00:29:37,973
Of course.

322
00:29:39,388 --> 00:29:43,339
One two three.

323
00:29:43,735 --> 00:29:47,480
One two three.

324
00:29:48,641 --> 00:29:50,205
One two…

325
00:29:51,471 --> 00:29:52,323
Here you are.

326
00:29:54,277 --> 00:29:55,473
Handsome.

327
00:30:04,863 --> 00:30:06,037
[Mr. Anantachai Lertwongsa - Credit Manager]

328
00:30:14,925 --> 00:30:15,977
Good afternoon.

329
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,348
Good afternoon.

330
00:30:20,455 --> 00:30:21,629
May I see the document?

331
00:30:34,903 --> 00:30:35,890
[Title Deed]

332
00:30:36,877 --> 00:30:38,280
What is your relationship with…

333
00:30:43,309 --> 00:30:44,574
this title deed’s owner?

334
00:30:46,902 --> 00:30:47,824
She’s my relative.

335
00:30:48,788 --> 00:30:49,958
May I know how you are related to her?

336
00:31:03,987 --> 00:31:05,712
